# Wayfinder Routing Rules

Proyek ini menggunakan **Laravel Wayfinder** untuk type-safe routing. Ikuti aturan berikut untuk menghindari error.

## Import Routes dengan Benar

### ❌ SALAH - Jangan import dari subfolder jika tidak ada export-nya

```typescript
// WRONG: login GET tidak di-export dari @/routes/login
import { login } from '@/routes/login';
```

### ✅ BENAR - Import dari lokasi yang tepat

```typescript
// Routes utama (home, dashboard, login GET, logout) ada di @/routes/index.ts
import { login, logout, dashboard, home } from '@/routes';

// Routes dengan subfolder (admin, profile, password, dll)
import { index, create, store, edit, update, destroy } from '@/routes/admin/users';
import { email, request, update as passwordUpdate } from '@/routes/password';
import { show as profileShow } from '@/routes/profile';
import { update as profilePasswordUpdate } from '@/routes/profile/password';
```

## Penggunaan dengan Inertia

### Link Component - Langsung pass Wayfinder function

```vue
<!-- ✅ BENAR: Link menerima Wayfinder object langsung -->
<Link :href="login()">Masuk</Link>
<Link :href="create()">Tambah User</Link>
<Link :href="edit(user.id)">Edit</Link>
```

### Router Methods - Gunakan `.url` property

```typescript
// ✅ BENAR: router.visit() butuh string URL
router.visit(edit.url(user.id));

// ✅ BENAR: router.get/post/delete butuh .url
router.get(index().url, filters, options);
router.delete(destroy(user.id).url);
router.post(store().url);

// ❌ SALAH: router.visit() tidak menerima object
router.visit(edit(user.id)); // ERROR!
```

### useForm - Gunakan `.url` property

```typescript
// ✅ BENAR
form.post(store().url, options);
form.put(update(user.id).url, options);

// ❌ SALAH
form.post(store(), options); // ERROR!
```

## Quick Reference

| Method | Accepts Object | Needs `.url` |
|--------|---------------|--------------|
| `<Link :href="">` | ✅ Yes | No |
| `router.visit()` | ❌ No | Yes |
| `router.get/post/put/delete()` | ❌ No | Yes |
| `form.post/put/patch/delete()` | ❌ No | Yes |

## Struktur Routes

```
@/routes/
├── index.ts          # home, dashboard, login (GET), logout
├── login/index.ts    # post (login POST only)
├── password/         # request, email, reset, update
├── profile/          # show, password/update
├── admin/
│   ├── users/        # index, create, store, edit, update, destroy, resetPassword, toggleStatus
│   └── audit-logs/   # index
└── ...
```
